imagingbook.calibration.zhang.NonlinearOptimizer

    imagingbook.calibration.zhang

    • Uses of NonlinearOptimizer in imagingbook.calibration.zhang

      Subclasses of NonlinearOptimizer in imagingbook.calibration.zhang 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  NonlinearOptimizerAnalytic
      Nonlinear optimizer based on the Levenberg-Marquart method, where the Jacobian matrix is calculated from analytic expressions (obtained with MatLab).
      class  NonlinearOptimizerNumeric
      Nonlinear optimizer based on the Levenberg-Marquart method, where the Jacobian matrix is calculated numerically (i.e., by estimating the first partial derivatives from finite differences).
